title: This TV Actor Was Injured While Rehearsing For Nach Baliye 8
text:
Sukriti Gumber Mar . 21 . 2017 Dipika Kakar, Shoaib Ibrahim 
Nach Baliye 8 will soon be back and so many of my absolute favourite TV jodis are participating in my all time favourite dance reality show. The couples have already started practicing their dance sequences, and one of them is Dipika Kakar and Shoaib Ibrahim . Unfortunately, Shoaib recently hurt himself during one of the practice sessions.
